  <official_title>Multicenter Summative Usability Study of Ciprofloxacin Dry Powder for Inhalation in Subjects With Non-Cystic Fibrosis Bronchiectasis (NCFB) or Chronic Obstructive Pulmonary Disease (COPD) Using Matching Placebo</official_title>
