  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The rationale of this study is to conduct a summative (i.e., validation) usability test of
      Ciprofloxacin Dry Powder for Inhalation (DPI) and the associated Instructions for Use.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
